{"pageProps":{"article":{"id":"6bc6281dca","title":"中共中央关于参加过蒋伪反动党团会门人员可否划为人民问题给华北局的批复","origin":"根据文件的翻印件打印","is_range_date":false,"dates":[{"id":"ada99cf03b","index":0,"year":1952,"month":1,"day":14,"articleId":"6bc6281dca"}],"tags":[{"id":"c9f57d6426","name":"文章","type":"文稿类型"}],"aliases":[],"publications":[{"id":"CCRD-shzygz","name":"中国五十年代初中期的政治运动数据库","internal":false,"official":false,"type":"db","author":"宋永毅","files":""}],"authors":[]},"publication_details":{"CCRD-shzygz":{"comments":[],"contents":[{"id":"a10e55c8e8","type":"title","text":"中共中央关于参加过蒋伪反动党团会门人员可否划为人民问题给华北局的批复","index":0,"publicationId":"CCRD-shzygz","articleId":"6bc6281dca"},{"id":"8ed14304e5","type":"appellation","text":"东北局，并告各中央局：","index":1,"publicationId":"CCRD-shzygz","articleId":"6bc6281dca"},{"id":"a142035f0d","type":"paragraph","text":"一月八日电悉。关于参加过蒋伪反动党团会门人员可否划为人民的问题，同意你们提出的意见。（东北局来电附后）","index":2,"publicationId":"CCRD-shzygz","articleId":"6bc6281dca"},{"id":"a7d22b8fab","type":"paragraph","text":" 中  央一九五二年一月十四日","index":3,"publicationId":"CCRD-shzygz","articleId":"6bc6281dca"},{"id":"6cf80c525c","type":"paragraph","text":"附：","index":4,"publicationId":"CCRD-shzygz","articleId":"6bc6281dca"},{"id":"cb05bf1eec","type":"subtitle","text":"东北局关于参加过蒋伪反动党团会门人员可否划为人民的请示","index":5,"publicationId":"CCRD-shzygz","articleId":"6bc6281dca"},{"id":"a23fed3927","type":"subtitle","text":"（一九五二年一月八日）","index":6,"publicationId":"CCRD-shzygz","articleId":"6bc6281dca"},{"id":"7cbfa55764","type":"appellation","text":"中央：","index":7,"publicationId":"CCRD-shzygz","articleId":"6bc6281dca"},{"id":"63a0d4365a","type":"paragraph","text":"辽东省委请示参加过蒋伪反动党团会门人员可否划为人民问题，我们意见：凡参加过蒋伪反动党团军政会门等人员，只要不是封建剥削阶级成分，而在解放前未担任重要反动职务，无重大反革命罪行，解放后守法劳动或从事其他正当职业者，应将其划为人民。妥否请批示。","index":8,"publicationId":"CCRD-shzygz","articleId":"6bc6281dca"},{"id":"42755da725","type":"paragraph","text":" 东北局一月八日","index":9,"publicationId":"CCRD-shzygz","articleId":"6bc6281dca"}],"page":{"id":"a68bf11bb0","publicationId":"CCRD-shzygz","articleId":